      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Daniel Anulliero</b>\n</p><p><b>Daniel Anulliero</b>,<br />\na French avocational computer games and chess programmer, who started programming in the 80s using a <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sharp_PC-1403\">SHARP PC 1403</a>, \nwhen he wrote an <a href=\"/Othello\" title=\"Othello\">Othello</a> program in <a href=\"/Basic\" title=\"Basic\">Basic</a>. Inspired by articles by <a href=\"/David_Levy\" title=\"David Levy\">David Levy</a>, he began chess programming on a <a href=\"/Macintosh\" title=\"Macintosh\">Macintosh</a> and wrote his first chess program in Basic, dubbed <i>BISHOP</i>, later ported to the <a href=\"/IBM_PC\" title=\"IBM PC\">PC</a> using <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/QuickBASIC\">QuickBASIC 4.5</a>. \nWhen he got aware of <a href=\"/Leo_Dijksman\" title=\"Leo Dijksman\">Leo Dijksman's</a> <a href=\"/WBEC\" title=\"WBEC\">WBEC Ridderkerk</a> tournament, Daniel Anulliero got hooked again, switched to the <a href=\"/C\" title=\"C\">C</a> programming language and started to write his first <a href=\"/Category:WinBoard\" title=\"Category:WinBoard\">WinBoard engine</a> <a href=\"/index.php?title=JARS&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"JARS (page does not exist)\">JARS</a>, later followed by <a href=\"/Yoda\" title=\"Yoda\">Yoda</a> \n<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>, <a href=\"/Isa\" title=\"Isa\">Isa</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> and most recently, but as of 2019 not officially released <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=BeLL&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"BeLL (page does not exist)\">BeLL</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2007_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2007 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2020_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2020 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Daniel_Anulliero&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2007_...\">2007 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Daniel_Anulliero&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2007 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=6255\">my presentation and help needed about winboard</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Anulliero</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, February 23, 2007</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=49232\">My new engine&#160;: Yoda</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Anulliero</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, June 02, 2008</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=4&amp;t=49818\">Tuning the eval</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Anulliero</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, January 02, 2009</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Daniel_Anulliero&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=4&amp;t=52394\">hashtables</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Anulliero</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, May 22, 2012&#160;» <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=49311\">about qs</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Anulliero</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 11, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Quiescence_Search\" title=\"Quiescence Search\">Quiescence Search</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=49556\">perft</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Anulliero</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 03, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Perft\" title=\"Perft\">Perft</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=53526\">Tuning eval</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Anulliero</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 01, 2014&#160;» <a href=\"/Automated_Tuning\" title=\"Automated Tuning\">Automated Tuning</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Daniel_Anulliero&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=55118\">knight's multiple atacks</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Anulliero</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 27, 2015</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=55192\">About the LCTII from the past</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Anulliero</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 02, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/LCT_II\" title=\"LCT II\">LCT II</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=55433\">bad eval for passers&#160;?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Anulliero</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 23, 2015</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=55526\">About LMR , again&#160;:-)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Anulliero</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 01, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Late_Move_Reductions\" title=\"Late Move Reductions\">Late Move Reductions</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=56690\">eval pieces</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Anulliero</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 15, 2015 </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=57384\">about pst</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Anulliero</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 26, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Piece-Square_Tables\" title=\"Piece-Square Tables\">Piece-Square Tables</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=57403\">about king attack</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Anulliero</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 27, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/King_Safety\" title=\"King Safety\">King Safety</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=57575\">high values of pst</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Anulliero</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 09, 2015</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=57998\">A funny bug&#160;:-)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Anulliero</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 19, 2015</li></ul>\n<p><b>2016</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=59426\">about hashtable</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Anulliero</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 04, 2016</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=59566\">hash eval, hash pawn or twice&#160;?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Anulliero</a>, March 19, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Evaluation_Hash_Table\" title=\"Evaluation Hash Table\">Evaluation Hash Table</a>, <a href=\"/Pawn_Hash_Table\" title=\"Pawn Hash Table\">Pawn Hash Table</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=59959\">Evaluate the pieces mobility</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Anulliero</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 25, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Mobility\" title=\"Mobility\">Mobility</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=61093\">Futility prunning</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Anulliero</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 11, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Futility_Pruning\" title=\"Futility Pruning\">Futility Pruning</a>, <a href=\"/Reverse_Futility_Pruning\" title=\"Reverse Futility Pruning\">Reverse Futility Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=61891\">Isa version 1.9.8 release</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Anulliero</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 30, 2016</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=62494\">Endgame bug in Isa</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Anulliero</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 15, 2016</li></ul>\n<p><b>2017</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=62802\">Search instability or&#160;?...</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Anulliero</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 12, 2017</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=63255\">Isa 1.9.63 release</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Anulliero</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 23, 2017</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=63606\">Isa 1.9.68 release</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Anulliero</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 01, 2017</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=63811\">Hash move and move ordering</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Anulliero</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 24, 2017</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=64078\">Isa 2.0.45 release</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Anulliero</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 25, 2017</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=65364\">Trading Pieces When Ahead In Material</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Anulliero</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 03, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Material\" title=\"Material\">Material</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=66040\">Isa 2.0.61 release</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Anulliero</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 17, 2017</li></ul>\n<p><b>2018 ...</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=66989\">Isa 2_0_64 Release</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Anulliero</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 01, 2018</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=68467\">Time out problems</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Anulliero</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\